# Flash Legal Funding

> Non-recourse pre-settlement funding for personal injury plaintiffs in the United States. No credit check, no monthly payments — if the case is lost, the client owes $0.

This site provides cash advances against pending personal injury settlements. Markdown mirrors of every page are available by appending `.md` (or replacing `index.html` with `index.md`) on any URL. A concatenated copy of all content is at {{ site }}/llms-full.txt.

## Core pages

- [Home — Flash Legal Funding]({{ site }}/index.md): Overview of pre-settlement funding, how it works, and case types funded.
- [How to Apply]({{ site }}/apply/index.md): Online application for pre-settlement funding.
- [Contact]({{ site }}/contact/index.md): Phone, email, and contact form for Flash Legal Funding.
- [FAQ]({{ site }}/faq/index.md): Detailed answers to common questions about lawsuit funding.
- [For Attorneys]({{ site }}/for-attorneys/index.md): Information for personal injury attorneys partnering with Flash Legal Funding.

